============================================================

Step 1:

Separate Implementation Class

```java
class GreetingImpl implements Greeting {

    @Override
    public void greet() {

        System.out.println("Hello");

    }
}
```


Step 2:

Anonymous Inner Class

```java
Greeting greeting = new Greeting() {

    @Override
    public void greet() {

        System.out.println("Hello");

    }

};
```


Step 3:

Lambda Expression

```java
Greeting greeting =
        () -> System.out.println("Hello");
```


Evolution:

```text
Separate Class
      ↓
Anonymous Inner Class
      ↓
Lambda Expression
```


