12. TYPE INFERENCE
============================================================

Java compiler Lambda parameters ke types target Functional Interface se infer kar sakta hai.


Interface:

```java
interface Calculator {

    int calculate(int a, int b);

}
```


Full:

```java
Calculator add =
        (int a, int b) -> a + b;
```


Short:

```java
Calculator add =
        (a, b) -> a + b;
```


