============================================================
26. BEHAVIOR PASSING
============================================================

Lambda ka powerful concept:

Behavior ko argument ki tarah pass kar sakte hain.


Example:

```java
interface Operation {

    int apply(int a, int b);

}
```


Method:

```java
static int calculate(
        int a,
        int b,
        Operation operation
) {

    return operation.apply(a, b);

}
```


Call:

```java
int result = calculate(
        10,
        20,
        (a, b) -> a + b
);
```


Yahan:

```java
(a, b) -> a + b
```

behavior argument ke form me pass hua.


Different behavior:

```java
calculate(
        10,
        20,
        (a, b) -> a * b
);
```


Same method:

```java
calculate()
```

Different behavior.


