27. VARIABLE CAPTURE
============================================================

Lambda surrounding scope ke local variables access kar sakta hai.


Example:

```java
int bonus = 1000;


Runnable task = () -> {

    System.out.println(bonus);

};
```


Ye valid hai.


Lekin local variable:

```java
bonus
```

final ya effectively final hona chahiye.


============================================================
28. EFFECTIVELY FINAL
============================================================

Example:

```java
int bonus = 1000;


Runnable task = () -> {

    System.out.println(bonus);

};
```


`bonus` explicitly final nahi hai:

```java
final int bonus = 1000;
```

Lekin value change nahi ho rahi.

Isliye ye:

```text
Effectively Final
```

hai.


Agar:

```java
int bonus = 1000;


Runnable task = () -> {

    System.out.println(bonus);

};


bonus = 2000;
```


Compile-time error ho sakta hai because captured local variable effectively final nahi raha.


