32. LIMITATIONS / IMPORTANT POINTS
============================================================

1. Lambda Functional Interface ke target context me use hota hai.

2. Interface me multiple abstract methods honge to same interface target ke roop me Lambda use nahi kar sakte.

3. Overly complex Lambda readability reduce kar sakta hai.

Bad:

```java
